The schedule for the selection process is being worked out as follows: -
table_trans: Advertisement in the newspaper by the Director / Registrar to invite proposals / applications for Dr. J.P. Naik Model State Teacher Award and issue circulars to all field offices.

Final Central Scrutiny Committee to submit the proposal to the Government / State Level Selection Committee.
